  PASSIVE_GAS_SPECIES
    O2(g)
  /
  
  MINERALS
    Smectite_MX80
    InertMineral
    Quartz
    Gypsum
    Pyrite
    Calcite
    Dolomite
    Siderite
    Clinochlore
    UO2:2H2O(am)
  /

